Date: Thu, 16 Apr 2026 05:17:28 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] fix(async): prevent face pipeline failures from
 concurrent MediaAiInsights updates

- FaceDetectionConsumer: persist faces in one transaction; append face_detection
  to services_completed in separate transactions with optimistic-lock retries
- PostAggregationTriggerService: include DB-backed mediaInsights JSON on
  post-aggregation-trigger so the Python aggregator does not miss ACKed stream history
---
